title: Good Luck, Father Ted
description: Father Dougal and Jack visit a Craggy Island fair filled with odd attractions, while Father Ted secretly tries to have a TV interview with "Faith Of Our Fathers".

title: Entertaining Father Stone
description: The always at a loss for words, Father Stone, visits Craggy Island and over stays his welcome.

title: The Passion of Saint Tibulus
description: Father Ted and Dougal protest a blasphemous new film on the orders of a visiting Bishop with a terrible secret.

title: Competition Time
description: Father Ted, Dougal and Jack enter a talent competition visited by a BBC presenter with an odd drinking problem.

title: And God Created Woman
description: Father Ted struggles with a crush he has for a lady visitor, and the arrival of a group of nuns.

title: Grant Unto Him Eternal Rest
description: Father Jack dies after drinking floor polish, leaving Ted and Dougal an inheritance.

title: Hell
description: Father Ted, Dougal and Jack take a holiday in a borrowed caravan.

title: Think Fast, Father Ted
description: Having to fix a roof leak, Father Ted tries a raffle to raise money.

title: Tentacles of Doom
description: Craggy Island gets a visit by three bishops who have come to upgrade a local holy relic.

title: Old Grey Whistle Theft
description: Father Ted and Jack go on a picnic, while Dougal makes friends with a local bad boy priest.

title: A Song for Europe
description: Father Ted and Dougal enter their song, "My Lovely Horse", into the Euro Song 96 contest.

title: The Plague
description: Bishop Len visits Craggy Island during a rabbit infestation.

title: Rock a Hula Ted
description: Father Ted hosts the "Lovely Girls Festival 96" , while Dougal gives the house away to a visiting feminist.

title: Cigarettes and Alcohol and Rollerblading
description: Father Ted ,Dougal and Jack try to give up their vices for Lent.

title: New Jack City
description: Father Ted and Dougal mistakenly celebrate when a sick Jack leaves, only to be replaced by someone worse.

title: Flight into Terror
description: While flying home from a trip with a group of priests, Father Ted's plane encounters trouble.

title: A Christmassy Ted
description: Father Ted wins the "Golden Cleric", for saving a fellow group of priests from an embarrassing situation.

title: Are You Right There Father Ted?
description: Father Ted holds a, "Celebration Of Craggy Island's Ethnic Diversity", party to prove he's not a racist.

title: Chirpy Burpy Cheap Sheep
description: Father Ted figures out the mystery of, "The Beast Of Craggy Island".

title: Speed 3
description: A local milkman seeks revenge after Father Ted gets him fired.

title: The Mainland
description: On a visit to the mainland, Mrs. Doyle and Father Jack get arrested while Ted and Dougal get lost in a cave.

title: Escape from Victory
description: Father Ted comes up with a scheme to win a football match against Father Dick Byrne.

title: Kicking Bishop Brennan up the Arse
description: After losing a bet to Father Dick Byrne, Father Ted has to kick Bishop Brennan up the backside.

title: Night of the Nearly Dead
description: After winning a poetry contest, Mrs. Doyle gets a visit by the shows host and a few of his crazed fans.

title: Going to America
description: After saving a fellow priest from suicide, Father Ted is invited to work at an American parish.
